                            </a>
                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/musume-ni-danzai-sareru-akuyaku-koushaku-ni-tensei-shitemashita-akuyaku-muubu-o-yameta-no-ni-nazeka-musume-ga-koori-no-reijou-ka-suru-ken"
                                    title="Musume Ni Danzai Sareru Akuyaku Koushaku Ni Tensei Shitemashita ~Akuyaku Muubu o Yameta no ni Nazeka Musume ga Koori No Reijou Ka Suru Ken~">Musume Ni Danzai Sareru Akuyaku Koushaku Ni Tensei Shitemashita ~Akuyaku Muubu o Yameta no ni Nazeka Musume ga Koori No Reijou Ka Suru Ken~</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 3.2"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/musume-ni-danzai-sareru-akuyaku-koushaku-ni-tensei-shitemashita-akuyaku-muubu-o-yameta-no-ni-nazeka-musume-ga-koori-no-reijou-ka-suru-ken/chapter-3-2">
                                Chapter 3.2
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">814</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>Mark Stuart had realized something terrifying: he had been reincarnated as the mid-boss in a game! In the original game, he was fated to be condemned by his daughter, Forsina, who was known as the Ice Princess. Reflecting on his past coldness toward her, he resolves to change his fate by earning her affection. Through his thoughtfulness and his actions as a duke, his daughter begins to regain her love and trust in her father, but he ends up going too far, and her love slowly becomes overwhelmingly heavy!? </p>
                              <div class="read-more-wrap">
                                <a class="read-more" href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/musume-ni-danzai-sareru-akuyaku-koushaku-ni-tensei-shitemashita-akuyaku-muubu-o-yameta-no-ni-nazeka-musume-ga-koori-no-reijou-ka-suru-ken" title>Read more</a>
                              </div>
                                                    </div>

                        
                        
                                                                    
                        <div class="list-comic-item-wrap">
                            <a data-id="27262" class="list-story-item bookmark_check cover"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/be-bop-highschool" title="Be-Bop-Highschool">
                                <img alt="Be-Bop-Highschool"
                                     class="lazy"
                                     src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/be-bop-highschool.webp"
                                     data-src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/be-bop-highschool.webp"
                                     width="120" height="170"
                                     loading="lazy"
                                     >
                            </a>
                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/be-bop-highschool"
                                    title="Be-Bop-Highschool">Be-Bop-Highschool</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 244"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/be-bop-highschool/chapter-244">
                                Chapter 244
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">1,696,007</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>The story revolves around the lives of two rough-and-tumble high school friends Kato Hiroshi and Nakama Toru, who seemed to make a habit of getting into trouble and starting up fights. In keeping with the spirit of the manga, Toru and Hiroshi sport slicked back 50&#039;s style perms and adopted exaggerated swaggers that made them comical and yet also oddly cool. The drama also features an assortment of outlandish characters who sport even weirder fashions and hairdos. To describe the action in this drama, think Fight Club meets The Breakfast Club. </p>
                              <div class="read-more-wrap">
                                <a class="read-more" href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/be-bop-highschool" title>Read more</a>
                              </div>
                                                    </div>

                        
                        
                                                                    
                        <div class="list-comic-item-wrap">
                            <a data-id="89368" class="list-story-item bookmark_check cover"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/the-possessed-evil-women" title="The Possessed Evil Women">
                                <img alt="The Possessed Evil Women"
                                     class="lazy"
