                                     data-src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/the-possessed-evil-women.webp"
                                     width="120" height="170"
                                     loading="lazy"
                                     >
                            </a>
                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/the-possessed-evil-women"
                                    title="The Possessed Evil Women">The Possessed Evil Women</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 60"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/the-possessed-evil-women/chapter-60">
                                Chapter 60
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">793</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>A demon lord from the underworld finds herself trapped in the body of a human “villainess” hated by her family and feared by society , despite having never committed a crime . With no memory of how she got there and her powers completely sealed, she decides to live as a human while uncovering the truth. However, the more she learns, the more baffling human behavior becomes—especially when even the innocent can be branded as monsters. </p>
                              <div class="read-more-wrap">
                                <a class="read-more" href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/the-possessed-evil-women" title>Read more</a>
                              </div>
                                                    </div>

                        
